phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common Material component mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Hardcoded TextField | Use `var text by remember { mutableStateOf("") }` |
| Missing onClick | Always provide onClick lambda |
| Missing onCheckedChange | Provide onCheckedChange |
| No dismiss handling | Handle onDismissRequest properly |
| Wrong colors | Use MaterialTheme colors |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Proper TextField
var text by remember { mutableStateOf("") }
OutlinedTextField(
    value = text,
    onValueChange = { text = it }
)

// 2. Button with onClick
Button(onClick = { /* action */ }) {
    Text("Click me")
}

// 3. Switch with onCheckedChange
var checked by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
Switch(
    checked = checked,
    onCheckedChange = { checked = it }
)

// 4. Dialog with dismiss
var showDialog by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
if (showDialog) {
    AlertDialog(
        onDismissRequest = { showDialog = false },
        confirmButton = { TextButton({ showDialog = false }) { Text("OK") } }
    )
}

// 5. Use Material colors
Button(
    onClick = {},
    colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(
        containerColor = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primary
    )
) {
    Text("Button")
}
```

